,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc9511755bbdb880dcce9af3d9cef1d1f1e6ca3b","tid":602234,"uid":39381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T01:39:52.000Z","msg":"今日會唔會上到5,000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T01:44:29.000Z","msg":"品<br />\n<br />\n唔會啦"},{"pid":"e3a9ca4169bc81a7d1ef746cd213aa45526da0de","tid":602234,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc9511755bbdb880dcce9af3d9cef1d1f1e6ca3b","tid":602234,"uid":39381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T01:39:52.000Z","msg":"今日會唔會上到5,000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T01:44:54.000Z","msg":"吹撚到去十萬"},{"pid":"8143307762d9e8302bc9af0eb7ec37f6ab65f604","tid":602234,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T01:48:47.000Z","msg":"最後原來係傳媒鳩吹"},{"pid":"a5b73f4d28453c5086611a26ece73822f5d9cf19","tid":602234,"uid":37976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T02:41:01.000Z","msg":"有線新聞 i-Cable News<br />\n<br />\n【預算案補漏方案】<br />\n【消息:18歲或以上市民可獲發$4000現金】<br />\n【預算案中受惠不足$4000者可獲發放差額】<br />\n<br />\n消息指政府最快今日公布預算案補漏方案。今次的補漏措施受惠範圍很闊，18歲或以上，不以收入劃線，辦理申請手續後可以獲發4千元現金津貼。在預算案中、受惠超過4千元的就不合資格。<br />\n<br />\n但如果受惠少於4千元，例如正領取綜援、生果金等等「出三糧」之後、金額仍不足4千可獲發差額。退稅、退差餉不足4千元的亦可獲補足。<br />\n<br />\n變左咁樣"},{"pid":"646839bd6d6f667b7ef16c2202845b847317b76d","tid":602234,"uid":103325,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T05:43:40.000Z","msg":"陳茂波落台啦，響政府咁多盈餘嘅情況下，都可以出到一份搞到民怨沸騰嘅財政預算案，佢真係無資格做官"},{"pid":"c901a6a591d1f1b1763895a2d2535c22d0732d70","tid":602234,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T05:49:06.000Z","msg":"在預算案中、受惠超過4千元的就不合資格<br />\n業主比差餉唔過4千有無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"9a11752564f408eb9fdc97c73fb54f2f15c75a25","tid":602234,"uid":10788,"like":0,"disl